sets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e7223bfccb212d596f95891d8b8d5ff0d6a2d5","tid":148680,"uid":35410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"小時候，美國是敵人，法國是敵人，英國是敵人，菲律賓越南韓國日本都是敵人&hellip;&hellip;後來，印度是敵人，&ldquo;老大哥&rdquo;蘇聯是敵人，就連同族兄弟的台灣也是敵人！我恨他們，我想當兵去打他們。慢慢的，我長大了，我百思不得其解：我們為什麼有這麼多敵人？現在，終於明白了：原來，我們是世界公敵！<br />\n<br />\n一個支那人得自白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2e3ed37aee96353c1d0b180bdac1e873560ccb","tid":148680,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fdbae67c0c3080517a24efbdf781112ca89a4e","tid":148680,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d6edcc36de7e7ce20ce5b6bbff001ab9a96c5b","tid":148680,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>差南及西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n菲律賓越南緬甸嗰班二打六三個臭皮匠頂住檔先</blockquote><br />\n印尼呢，想打柒班仆街好耐"},{"pid":"bf4fd56f31c0a51c87498d4296b5617d0297fcd8","tid":148680,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:20:13.000Z","msg":"支那柒夠未"},{"pid":"a96fd6e82fbf1ce9036361d082f399ccddff8e4f","tid":148680,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"支那狗對住南韓就瓜瓜嘈<br />\n見到俄羅斯就嚇到屁滾尿流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65338cf81efdcbc6c613170d00123f26432d6a21","tid":148680,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"反俄未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdc